Usage: place_design [-help] [-concurrent_macros] [-incremental]
                    [-noPrePlaceOpt] [-sdp]

-help                                     # Prints out the command usage
-concurrent_macros                        # mixed size placement
                                          # (bool, optional)
-incremental                              # Incremental placement
                                          # (bool, optional)
-noPrePlaceOpt                            # Disable pre-place optimization
                                          # (bool, optional)
-sdp                                      # Enables SDP-aware (Structured Data
                                          # Path) placement (bool, optional)